name: "Allo" Card
description:
The perfect card for a quick note to a friend! 
"алло" is an informal way of answering the phone (hello) in Russian. 

3.5x5 folded note card printed on eco friendly bamboo paper. Comes with a matching white envelope.

name: Craft Kit - Shield
description:
Design your own shield with this kit that includes a kid size shield hand made from reclaimed wood. Comes pre primed and ready to paint. Includes large size paintbrush, assortment of non toxic paints and a leaflet showing traditional Russian historic designs.  
Please note, shields are individually cut from reclaimed wood and may show the natural texture of its original state.

name: Craft Kit - Greeting Cards
description: This kit include 2 5x7 Letterpress printed Greeting Cards, matching envelopes and colored pencils in an assortment of colors. Designs include a Matryoshka and a traditional Russian "Firebird"

name: Craft Kit - Cookie Decorating
description: Cookie decorating kit comes in either "Matryoshkas" style or "Sword and Shield" Includes frosting mix with instructions, sugar crystals and decorative candy.

name: Craft Kit - Kokoshniki
description: Design your own Kokoshnik, traditional Russian Head-dress. Comes with Kokoshnik base, ribbon assortment, and rhinestones.

name: Craft Kit - Matryoshka Nesting Dolls
description: Design your own Matryoshka nesting dolls with this kit that comes with 3 pieces to paint, Paintbrushes in 2 sizes, non toxic paints and a art sample leaflet to help you get started.

name: Pascha Kulich
description:
There is something about letterpress that is so delicious. Making you want to sink your teeth into it, or bathe in it... or at least get your hands on it. When you touch something that has been printed on letterpress, you know it is different. It has texture. You can feel that it takes a lot of skill, patience and craftsmanship to create the final product.
It takes you away from the mass-produced.

Letterpress is one of the oldest methods of printing where ink is applied to a raised surface and is then pressed onto paper, leaving an impression.

Letterpress printed with love on eco friendly bamboo
4.25 x 5.5 folded card with matching white envelope
Hand mixed inks

name: Sweet Namesday
description: Letterpress cards are printed with (tons of) love on an antique Chandler and Price platen press. The eco friendly bamboo paper has a fluffy appearance that takes a "bite" of each design deeply, giving every card a three dimensional and luxurious feel. We use hand mixed inks in beautiful, rich colors. Each card is printed individually and has its own unique character.
